videos.description: Heralded Stanford freshman Ziaire Williams comes up with a steal on defense and then knocks down a 3-pointer on the other end for his first collegiate bucket.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Ziaire Williams splashes 3 to get Stanford on the board) 2020/11/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Ziaire Williams splashes 3 to get Stanford on the board

videos.description: Stanford guard Bryce Wills gets a deflection on defense and runs the floor to finish with a slam dunk on the other end.
